Package net.canarymod.tasks

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TaskOwner
    Interface for defining a ServerTask owner

    Has no other use outside of the ServerTask
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ServerTask
    Server Task

    Extend this class to add synchronized tasks to the Server queue.
    Task are set to execute along with the Server's main thread.
    Exact timing is not guaranteed, and based on how often the Server ticks.
    ServerTaskManager
    Server Task Manager

    The Manager for ServerTask
    If an exception occurs while running a task, it gets removed from the queue, regardless of continuous status
